  "text": "The Aedes mosquito is a crescent public health concern, and its control or eradication is urgent. The available or in development control methods can be divided into five categories: 1 -environmental breeding sites control; 2 -mechanical traps; 3 -insect fertility reduction technique; 4 -insecticides; and 5 -transgenic insect. [CITATION_1] ",
